# LinkedIn Organic Content Strategy for B2B SaaS

## Objective

Research proven B2B SaaS operators who use LinkedIn to build audience, trust, and pipeline.

## Project Structure

- research/sources.md
- research/linkedin-posts/
- research/youtube-transcripts/
- research/other/

## Why This Topic

LinkedIn is one of the highest-leverage organic growth channels for B2B SaaS.

## Initial Insights

1. Strong hooks increase attention
2. Founder-led content builds trust
3. Consistency compounds authority
4. Clear positioning improves engagement
5. Educational content performs best